90
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:58,959
Shaq does have endorsement deals in China.

91
00:03:58,959 --> 00:04:01,520
So he’s putting his money where his mouth
is.

92
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,930
And Shaq is no sellout.

93
00:04:03,930 --> 00:04:07,290
Thanks for playing this edition of Sellout
or No Sellout.

94
00:04:07,290 --> 00:04:08,739
